    },
    {
        "Key": 145,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "晴霆光",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "那……我做得应该还可以吧？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 146,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "如果非得评价一番，那晴的动作自然是生涩且僵硬的……但正因是晴，我更愿意用羞涩且温柔来形容。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 147,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "——而蛋包饭的口感便因此更添几分风味了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 148,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我知道这种评价带上了我的小私心，但那又如何呢？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 149,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "见晴过了许久也没有收回手的意思，我口中含着那根勺子，心想着是不是该提醒她一下。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "b-8",
        "Flag": "b-8",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 150,
        "Flag": "b-8-1",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "提醒她",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 151,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "至少在我看来，你做得挺好的，唯一的缺点就是勺子不是很好吃。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 152,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "由于勺子还插在我嘴里的缘故，这句话说出来有些含混不清。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 153,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "晴这才像是意识到了自己的动作的疏漏，连忙抽回了手，神色局促地抿着嘴唇，眼睛不知道该看向哪儿。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 154,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "于是她的声音也飘飘忽忽的，找不到重心。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 155,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "晴霆光",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我还不太熟练……我会勤于练习，下次会做得更好的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 156,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "晴霆光",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我是说……下一次约会的时候会让你看到的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 157,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "或许是性格使然，晴在这一类事情上真是出乎意料的笨拙，但……我很喜欢这样的晴。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 158,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我甚至很希望自己能更多地了解这样的她。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 159,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 160,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "回到房间，我脑海中依旧浮现着晴的模样。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 161,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "笨拙的行为、慌乱的神色、娇羞的模样、脸颊那不自然的红晕、以及时不时含混不清的话语——这都不是我认识的那个晴。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 162,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "晴似乎……有点奇怪？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 163,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她变得有些别扭了？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 164,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "或者说……在某些事情上更认真了？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 165,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "怀着这样的担忧，我于当天晚上选了个寂静的时分前去问候。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 166,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "但我并未能寻到晴的身影，空空如也的房间里只有郁金香的气味萦绕在我的鼻尖，当我想要抓住它时，它转瞬间又消失不见。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 167,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "晴并不在房间里。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 168,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "想来她应该只能在那个地方了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 169,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我看着训练室虚掩的大门，心里的答案有了回应。",
        "disable": 0
    },
